data.description:
Wow! What a beautiful custom home and property! Located in a lovely neighborhood just off Empire Grade, this sprawling single level home sits on over an acre of flat useable ground. Plenty of space for everyone and ALL hobbies! 
Inside you will love the vaulted ceilings in the living room and its cheery pellet stove and lots of windows bringing in natural light.
The kitchen with stainless steel appliances and plenty of beautiful wood cupboards flows easily into the family room with a lovely brick fireplace and hearth. Step out to the large Sunroom off the dining area. 
The primary bedroom suite offers a large walk-in closet and full En Suite. Down the hall you will find two additional guest bedrooms, a full guest bath with tub, and dedicated laundry room.
But wait there is more! There is a huge bonus room with Vaulted ceilings and access to the back deck. 
Home has a 2-car attached garage, but thats not all - follow the garden path and you will find an extraordinary workshop with drive-through capabilities! Possibilities of putting another driveway to connect directly to Empire Grade, or perhaps convert to ADU? 
This is seriously a special property!
